OL,3,CWildfire warnings as crews remain at
OL,4,Cscene of large heath fire
OL,6,FFire crews are continuing to tackle
OL,7,Fhotspots following a large heath fire
OL,8,Fnear Camberley.
OL,10,FThe alarm was raised at 1.30pm on
OL,11,FSaturday July 11th and multiple crews
OL,12,Ffrom Hampshire and Surrey were
OL,13,Fmobilised to Blackwater.
OL,15,FAt its height, the fire spread to
OL,16,Fapproximately 10 hectares, (25 acres)
OL,17,Fof heathland.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
