OL,3,CWildfire warnings as crews remain at
OL,4,Cscene of large heath fire
OL,6,FNine fire engines, three water
OL,7,Fcarriers, four Land Rover support
OL,8,Fvehicles and a range of specialist
OL,9,Fwildfire vehicles attended.
OL,11,FFirefighters used hose reels and
OL,12,Fspecialist wildfire equipment to bring
OL,13,Fthe fire under control and prevent
OL,14,Ffurther spread.
OL,16,FPolice closed nearby roads, and
OL,17,Fmembers of the public were asked to
OL,18,Favoid the area while emergency
OL,19,Fservices worked safely to contain the
OL,20,Ffire.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
