OL,3,CWildfire warnings as crews remain at
OL,4,Cscene of large heath fire
OL,6,FThroughout the night and into the
OL,7,Fearly hours of Sunday morning, crews
OL,8,Fcontinued to extinguish remaining
OL,9,Fhotspots and dampen down the affected
OL,10,Farea.
OL,12,FCrews are expected to maintain a
OL,13,Fpresence at the scene throughout today
OL,14,Fwhile they continue to monitor for any
OL,15,Fremaining hotspots and ensure the
OL,16,Faffected area remains safe.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
