OL,3,CWildfire warnings as crews remain at
OL,4,Cscene of large heath fire
OL,6,FFire services across the south have
OL,7,Fwarned of an increased risk of
OL,8,Fwildfires because of the tinder-like
OL,9,Fconditions, as the country experiences
OL,10,Fits third heatwave of the year.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/4
